      <title>中国债券市场关注重要立法会议的财政计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-bond-market-eyes-fiscal-plans-from-key-legislative-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国债券交易员正在关注本周的一次重要立法会议，预计立法者将在会议上批准一项价值数万亿元人民币的财政方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-bond-market-eyes-fiscal-plans-from-key-legislative-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 01:11:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产债务违约风险跃升至 2023 年 3 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/nissan-s-debt-default-risk-jumps-to-highest-since-march-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本汽车制造商日产汽车公司大幅下调盈利预期并宣布将裁员 9,000 人之后，该公司信用风险指标跃升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/nissan-s-debt-default-risk-jumps-to-highest-since-march-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 00:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛克哈特：“有信心”美联储独立性将得到维护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/lockhart-confident-federal-reserve-independence-will-be-preserved</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前亚特兰大联邦储备银行行长丹尼斯·洛克哈特分享了他对央行决定将利率降低四分之一个百分点的看法。他还讨论了美联储的独立性。主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普连任，他不会辞职。洛克哈特在“彭博：亚洲交易”节目中发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/lockhart-confident-federal-reserve-independence-will-be-preserved</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 00:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场消化特朗普和中国影响 油价有望本周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着市场消化特朗普第二次当选总统的影响，包括是否会刺激第一大进口国中国扩大刺激措施，油价本周上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国将积极应对选举后市场波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/korea-vows-active-response-to-post-us-election-market-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国表示，将加强对金融市场的监控，并“积极”应对，以缓解过度波动，因为政策制定者正在为唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫的影响做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/korea-vows-active-response-to-post-us-election-market-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
